  "id": "019d286a-f2d7-7750-81b8-3390b25d84a5",
  "content": "### Bug fix: Route existing search through pipeline\n### AppState update\n\n## Dependency Chain\n\n```\nM3  (GraphStore impl)  ──┐\n                          ├──► M3.2 (RAG Pipeline)\nM3.1 (GenerationEngine) ─┘\n```\n\nM3.2 can partially function without M3.1 — `context()` mode works without `GenerationEngine`. Only `ask()` mode requires M3.1.\n\n\n## Test Strategy\n\n| Component | Approach |\n|-----------|----------|\n| `VectorRetriever` | Unit test: MockEngine + LiteStore (same pattern as ContextBuilder tests) |\n| `GraphExpandRetriever` | Unit test: MockEngine + LiteStore + LiteGraphStore |\n| `StructuredAugmenter` | Pure unit test: `Vec<SearchResult>` → formatted string, no I/O |\n| `TokenEstimator` | Unit test: chars/4 heuristic, budget enforcement |\n| `RagPipeline` | Integration test: mock all three traits, verify orchestration + trace |\n| REST/MCP endpoints | Extend existing server tests with new endpoints |\n| E2E with Ollama | Integration test (skip if unavailable): full vector → augment → generate |",
  "source_version": "docs/rfcs/2026-03-02-m3.2-rag-pipeline-design.md",
